DESCRIPTION:Embark on an exhilarating climbing adventure at Pilot Mountain 
 State Park. Whether you're stepping into outdoor climbing for the first tim
 e or seeking new challenges as an experienced climber\, Pilot Mountain offe
 rs a range of routes to suit every level. Discover the thrill of scaling on
 e of North Carolina’s most popular climbing destinations.  With transportat
 ion\, lunch\, gear\, and instruction provided\, this trip promises an unfor
 gettable day of achievement and camaraderie in the great outdoors.
DTEND:20260225T230000Z
