BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Meetings and Conferences
DESCRIPTION:Join the Institute for Emerging Issues for the 2026 Emerging Is
 sues Forum: Future Forward Water. North Carolina’s economic vitality depend
 s on how we manage our water systems today. From aging infrastructure and e
 merging contaminants to workforce shortages and storm resilience\, this mul
 ti-city event offers attendees a unique opportunity to connect locally and 
 tackle our state’s most pressing water challenges. This event also marks th
 e 40th anniversary of the Emerging Issues Forum and is the second installme
 nt of the 2025-2027 Future Forward Infrastructure series.  Founded by forme
 r North Carolina Governor and NC State alumnus Jim Hunt\, the Emerging Issu
 es Forum brings thought leaders together to address critical challenges in 
 North Carolina and implement solutions that drive the state forward.\n\nGet
  your tickets\, view the agenda and learn more about the forum locations on
  the forum website.
DTEND:20260225T203000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025710Z
DTSTART:20260225T143000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:2026 Emerging Issues Forum: Future Forward Water
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51897405102606
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/2026-emerging-issues-forum-future-forwa
 rd-water
END:VEVENT
