DESCRIPTION:Join the Department of World Languages and Cultures for an open
  house. Stop by to explore everything the department has to offer\, includi
 ng courses\, student clubs\, study abroad programs and more.\n\nIf you are 
 thinking about adding a major\, minor or certificate\, this is the perfect 
 chance to ask questions about our department\, meet professors and students
  and see what might fit your goals. If you are thinking about attending gra
 duate school\, come learn about our graduate programs\, including our accel
 erated bachelor-to-master program. \n\nThe open house will include a raffle
  of gift certificates to campus stores and coffee shops and other fun prize
 s. You can earn up to five raffle entries. Here's how:\n\nRegister to atten
 d the open house to earn one raffle entry.Attend the open house to earn one
  raffle entry.Complete the Passport Journey at the open house by chatting w
 ith faculty and students to earn three raffle entries.
