X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:In a virtual two-part workshop\, the Graduate School will provi
 de strategies for planning and managing a writing project and fundamental t
 ips for structuring writing for a variety of contexts. Participants will cl
 arify their writing goals for the semester and learn strategies to implemen
 t on current and future writing projects. We will use different genres of w
 riting as case studies\, so participants can learn tips for summarizing\, p
 araphrasing and synthesizing their writing projects.
