 ctivity. You'll choose the purpose for your journal — art\, writing\, organ
 izing\, gratitude\, etc. — and put together the papers and inserts that wor
 k for you. We will coil-bind them using old book covers that you can custom
 ize or leave as is. Once you create your journal\, you can fill it using sc
 rapbook paper\, stickers\, washi tape\, markers and more to create a mixed-
