BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Performances,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Ballet teacher Oliver Beres will lead a class that will focus o
 n the Vaganova technique with a blend of Balanchine style. The class will w
 ork on placement\, technique and turnout\, with a strong emphasis on musica
 lity. The session will begin with intermediate barre work\, starting at pli
 es and finishing with grand battements. Center exercises and across-the-flo
 or combinations that will incorporate a mix of adagio\, turning combination
 s and jumping will also be part of the session.\n\nBéres was born in Hungar
 y and began his dance training in 1996 at age 11 when he was accepted into 
 the Hungarian National Dance Academy. During his education\, Béres was one 
 of the four students chosen to perform with the Hungarian National Ballet. 
 He was an apprentice in the company from age 14 until he graduated from the
  school in 2005. During his nine years of education\, he had the privilege 
 of training under many great teachers\, including Zoltan Solymosi\, who was
  a principal dancer with the Royal Ballet. Beres has performed in several c
 ountries in Europe\, including Romania\, Slovakia\, Poland\, Czech Republic
 \, Austria and Italy. After graduation\, he was offered a full scholarship 
 with the North Carolina Dance Theatre in Charlotte\, which brought him to t
 he United States. He has danced with the Hungarian National Ballet\, Slovak
  State Opera House\, New Jersey Ballet and Carolina Ballet. He has performe
 d several soloist and principal roles\, including Firebird\, Swan Lake\, Do
 n Quixote and many more. He retired as a soloist with Carolina Ballet in 20
 17 after dancing with the company for nine years. Béres is currently a full
 -time ballet teacher.
DTEND:20260305T234500Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025711Z
DTSTART:20260305T223000Z
GEO:35.783875;-78.673114
LOCATION:Wellness and Recreation Center and Carmichael Gym\, 2307
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Ballet With Oliver Beres
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52075094329870
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/ballet-wirh-oliver-beres
END:VEVENT
