BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Films
DESCRIPTION:What if you could erase all your pain? Would you do it? Afloat\
 , a film that follows Owen\, a young man burdened by shame\, fear and traum
 a\, who returns home and takes an experimental pill meant to erase emotiona
 l pain. What he hopes will heal him only makes things worse. Written and di
 rected by Tae Park\, a North Carolina filmmaker and NC State alum\, and wit
 h cast and crew from the Triangle’s creative scene\, Afloat explores the qu
 iet\, invisible battles of healing. \n\nThe film's runtime is 26 minutes. I
 t will be followed by a Q&A with Park.
DTEND:20260306T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025711Z
DTSTART:20260305T233000Z
