 thically\, creatively and practically?\n\nThe College of Humanities and Soc
 ial Sciences invites students from all majors and backgrounds who want to b
 etter understand generative AI and how it's used in communication\, strateg
 y and real-world contexts to attend its AI Literacy Workshop. If you comple
 te the workshop\, you'll receive a certificate of completion.\n\nRegistrati
