BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life,Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Parents and Families Services is excited to partner with the Di
 vision of Academic and Student Affairs to host a race that will serve as a 
 fundraiser in support of NC State’s Feed the Pack Food Pantry. A portion of
  all proceeds will go to Feed the Pack.\n\nJust shy of a 5k\, the 2.9-mile 
 race will start and end around beautiful Lake Raleigh on NC State’s Centenn
 ial Campus. Timing and tracking will not be recorded formally. Participants
  interested in time-tracking will need to plan to do so independently. \n\n
 A $30 registration fee is required to participate in the race.  Here is wha
 t’s included in your registration:\n\nT-shirtWater bottleRace bib Finisher’
 s medalAll items will be distributed at check-in on race day.\n\nRace parti
 cipants are encouraged to wear fruit and vegetable costumes. Please bring n
 onperishable food donations for Feed the Pack and to be entered win prizes.
DTEND:20260308T140000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025711Z
DTSTART:20260308T123000Z
GEO:35.767879;-78.677586
LOCATION:Lake Raleigh
