 t puppetry\, dance and music\, has charmed audiences across the globe and w
 as even a semi-finalist on NBC’s America’s Got Talent.\n\nLightwire's Dino-
 Light shares the story of a scientist who brings a friendly dinosaur to lif
 e. The show is recommended for all who have a sense of wonder\, especially 
 children 6 to 10 years old and their parents.
