BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:Join the Women's Center for The Flame of HerStory\, a vision ga
 llery inspired by the spirit of the Olympics and the legends of Greek mytho
