DESCRIPTION:What better way to close out our 2025/26 mainstage series than 
 with a beloved artist and friend\, John Pizzarelli?  Widely recognized as a
  leading contemporary interpreter of the Great American Songbook\, Pizzarel
 li\, a Grammy Award-winning guitarist and singer\, has been lauded by the B
 oston Globe for his “reinvigoration” of the genre. Pizzarelli’s expansive r
 epertoire now includes the music of iconic artists\, such as Joni Mitchell\
 , Neil Young\, Tom Waits\, Antônio Carlos Jobim and The Beatles.\n\nDid we 
 also mention that he is an absolutely magnetic human being and an NC State 
 LIVE fan-favorite? Prepare to be delighted by both the artist and his maste
 rful renditions of your favorite tunes\, and join us for a night you won’t 
 soon forget.
DTEND:20260315T003000Z
