BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:Design takes a community. Here in the College of Design\, we st
 rive to support every member of our community\, whether they are students p
 reparing to be professionals\, innovators answering the questions that will
  shape our future\, faculty researching world problems\, or our engaged net
 work of mentors and supporters.\n\nWe’re asking you to join us on March 25 
 for Day of Giving — a 24-hour campaign to help our college\, and everyone w
 ho is part of it\, thrive. We hope that you reflect on your personal connec
 tion to the College of Design and how your support allows our community mem
 bers to explore their own passions. \n\nHow can you help? Here are a few wa
 ys to make a big impact:\n\nMark March 25 on your calendars. Make a gift. C
 onsider making a gift to fuel our students’ passions.Ask your network to gi
 ve. The strength of our Pack can help us achieve collective success.If you 
 don’t already\, follow us on social media (Facebook\, Instagram and LinkedI
 n). We will be sharing reminders about Day of Giving in addition to telling
  stories of how your generosity touches all aspects of the college.
DTEND:20260326T035900Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025711Z
DTSTART:20260325T050000Z
