BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life,Information Session,High-Impact Ex
 periences
DESCRIPTION:As part of NC State’s Fulbright Week celebration\, the Office o
 f Global Engagement\, the Office for Faculty Excellence and the University 
 Fellowships Office invite you to attend the Fulbright Networking Reception.
 \n\nThis special event will bring together former and current Fulbright stu
 dents\, faculty and scholars to celebrate the research\, teaching and globa
 l experiences made possible through the Fulbright Program. It is an opportu
 nity to connect with university community members who have participated in 
 Fulbright exchanges and to learn more about these transformative experience
 s.\n\nThe event will also include remarks on Fulbright’s mission for global
  initiatives by Vice Provost for Global Engagement Amy Conger and Vice Prov
 ost of Faculty Excellence Kim Grainger and a slideshow of Fulbright experie
 nces. Hors d’oeuvres will be available for guests.\n\nThe Fulbright Associa
 tion is the sponsor of this event.\n\nPlease join us throughout Fulbright W
 eek\, which is March 30-April 3\, for more informative and engaging events 
 highlighting the Fulbright Program’s 80th year of global collaboration and 
 providing life-changing opportunities for students\, faculty and scholars.\
 n\nFulbright is an academic and cultural exchange program that enables Amer
 ican students\, faculty and professionals to study\, teach and conduct rese
 arch in more than 160 partner countries worldwide. The experiences foster l
 asting connections\, strengthen mutual understanding and support collaborat
 ive solutions to global challenges.
DTEND:20260402T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025712Z
DTSTART:20260402T190000Z
GEO:35.784114;-78.671321
LOCATION:Talley Student Union\, 3210
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Fulbright Networking Reception 
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52276835955991
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/fulbright-networking-reception
END:VEVENT
