X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Confidence can make all the difference in your career\, but it’
 s not always easy to feel it. Self-doubt\, hesitation and imposter syndrome
  can hold you back from showing up as your best self. In this interactive w
 orkshop hosted by the Graduate School's Accelerate to Industry+ (A2i+) prog
 ram\, you’ll learn practical strategies to boost your presence\, speak with
  clarity and project confidence as you take the next step in your career. W
 hether you’re getting ready for interviews\, stepping into a leadership rol
 e or looking to grow where you are\, you’ll walk away with tools to shift y
 our mindset\, own your strengths and present yourself with confidence.
DTEND:20260402T213000Z
