BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:Join the NC State entrepreneurship community at the Coastal Bal
 lroom in Talley Student Union for the 2026 VenturePack Challenge Award Cere
 mony.\n\nVenturePack Challenge is Innovation and Entrepreneurship's largest
  entrepreneurship competition of the year. The challenge awards startup pac
 kages to student teams\, including a combination of cash\, mentorship and r
 esources they'll need to take their ventures to the next level. Join us Apr
 il 7 to witness the competition finale. Come hear live pitches and a Q&A wi
 th the judges and get inspired by some of our very best entrepreneurs at NC
  State. Plus\, vote for your favorite team to send them home with the Audie
 nce Choice Award.\n\nThe challenge will include an awards ceremony.\n\nLive
  student pitches: Come witness some of our top entrepreneurs pitch live and
  see how they tackle the Q&A with the judges.Audience choice voting: You ca
 n help your favorite team win the Audience Choice Award.Awards: Student tea
 ms will receive startup packages.The event will also feature an entrepreneu
 rship showcase.\n\nStartup exhibition and networking:  Come network with in
 novators and entrepreneurs and the finalist teams during a science fair-sty
 le exhibition.Refreshments: Enjoy free food and drinks at the exhibition an
 d a networking event after the awards show.Mr. and Ms. Wuf: Come take a pic
 ture with Mr. and Ms. Wuf while they roam around.Meet NC State alumni: Conn
 ect with fellow alumni and catch up on what they have been up to.This event
  is open to the public\, but please reserve your free ticket to attend.
DTEND:20260408T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025712Z
DTSTART:20260407T213000Z
