 tal health. Faculty\, staff\, students and members of the public can attend
  this celebration of One Health research and leadership at NC State. The sy
 mposium will feature:\n\nA keynote presentation from Tony Goldberg (Univers
 ity of Wisconsin-Madison)Research talks from the 2025-26 Global One Health 
 FellowsAn engaging panel discussion on topics at the food-water interfaceRe
 search sharing opportunities\, including a poster session and paper of the 
 year awardBe sure to stay afterwards for a one-hour reception with refreshm
 ents and plenty of networking.
