BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:The Women's Center will offer an opportunity to create genogram
 s and learn about their history. A genogram is a graphic representation of 
 a family tree that shows relationships within a family. Participants in the
  genogram session will explore hereditary patterns and psychological factor
 s highlighted in relationships. There may be conversations about healthy an
 d unhealthy relationships\, but there is no requirement to participate or s
 hare. Two counselors from the Counseling Center will be available for anyon
 e who needs support.\n\nThe genogram session is part of the university's pr
 ogramming for Sexual Assault Awareness Month.
