BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:The Lavender Celebration of Graduates is a nationwide event hel
 d by colleges and universities to recognize LGBTQ and allied graduates. Fam
 ily and friends cheer these exemplary graduates as each is honored using th
 eir correct names and pronouns.\n\nPlease register to ensure your spot at t
 he celebration at NC State. Registration will close when we reach maximum c
 apacity or on April 2\, whichever comes first. Everyone who plans to attend
  the celebration should complete a registration form\, including graduating
  students\, non-graduating students\, friends and family of graduates\, vol
 unteers and community members.\n\nThree awards are given out annually at th
 e celebration. You can nominate yourself or someone else you believe embodi
 es the spirit of each award. The deadline to complete the nomination form i
 s Friday\, March 13.\n\nVisit the LGBTQ Pride Center website for more infor
 mation. All students are welcome to attend.
DTEND:20260417T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025712Z
DTSTART:20260416T220000Z
GEO:35.784114;-78.671321
LOCATION:Talley Student Union\, Mountains Piedmont Ballroom
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Lavender Celebration
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51887005291155
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/lavender-celebration
END:VEVENT
