DESCRIPTION:FoodCon is a conference that brings together industry leaders a
 nd innovators to explore trends\, share insights and drive solutions for th
 e future of food. This conference is co-hosted by MBA students passionate a
 bout food\, agribusiness and sustainability from the NC State Poole College
  of Management\, the Duke University Fuqua School of Business and the Unive
 rsity of North Carolina at Chapel Hill's Kenan-Flagler School of Business.\
 n\nOur food system drives economic growth\, sustainability and social equit
 y. With food demand set to rise 50% by 2050\, innovation is crucial. FoodCo
 n empowers future leaders to tackle challenges\, such as food insecurity an
 d climate change while creating economic value.
