DESCRIPTION:Join the Friends of the Libraries as we celebrate the opening o
 f the newest student-curated exhibit in the Special Collections Exhibit Gal
 lery. Come learn about the development of natural history as reflected in t
 he Special Collections Research Center Rare Books collection. The exhibit t
 races the development of scientific knowledge and printing technology and c
 onsiders who did the work of natural history. \n\nThe celebration will feat
 ure remarks from the NC State University Libraries exhibits team and an opp
 ortunity to create your own botanical print to take home with you.\n\nHors 
 d’oeuvres will be served.
