DESCRIPTION:Reach for the Stars! Be a Star! is a STEM and resource fair for
  middle and high school students with disabilities\, and their families and
  friends\, to explore how to use their many abilities and talents to be par
 t of a diverse\, inclusive and innovative STEM workforce.\n\nIt will includ
 e hands-on STEM activities\, STEM educational and career pathways\, STEM co
 ntent\, skills and research\, STEM professionals with disabilities and comm
 unity resources.\n\n﻿This event is free and open to the community. Families
  are encouraged to attend.
