BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Challenge yourself on an exhilarating high ropes course nestled
  within NC State University’s scenic Schenck Forest. Set among towering tre
 es\, this course offers a unique outdoor experience designed to test your l
 imits\, build confidence and give you a taste of adventure. Suspended high 
 above the forest floor\, you'll navigate a series of thrilling obstacles an
 d zip lines\, all while surrounded by the natural beauty of Schenck Forest.
  Perfect for adventure seekers of all skill levels\, this adventure promise
 s an unforgettable day of achievement\, connection and fun in a beautiful w
 oodland setting.
DTEND:20260419T210000Z
