X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:The Emerging Designers Textile howcase highlights the work of s
 enior textile design students in the fashion and textile design (FTD) progr
 am at the Wilson College of Textiles\, celebrating the culmination of a sem
 ester-long capstone experience rooted in exploration\, experimentation and 
 refinement. Designers navigate the balance between creative freedom and cre
 ative discipline while leveraging access to state-of-the-art labs and studi
 os. Collections span home textiles\, apparel\, fiber art and more. \n\nThe 
 Emerging Designers Textile Showcase will be held at the Textiles Campus on 
 Centennial Campus.\n\nThe Textile Showcase Opening is on Sunday\, April 19\
 , from 3 to 5 p.m. The event is open to the public and free for all.\n\nThe
  Textile Showcase will also be open:\n- Monday\, April 20\, 8 a.m. to 5 p.m
 .\n- Tuesday\, April 21\, 8 a.m. to 5 p.m.\n- Wednesday\, April 22\, 8 a.m.
  to 5 p.m.
