CATEGORIES:Community Events
DESCRIPTION:Join the Italian Club and Italian Honor Society in the Departme
 nt of World Languages and Cultures for our end-of-the-semester potluck dinn
 er. We've planned a relaxed evening to celebrate the end of the term\, enjo
