DESCRIPTION:Join NC State for a celebration of sustainability accomplishmen
 ts on Tuesday\, April 21\, 2026. This annual event honors the people\, proj
 ects and progress that advance sustainability at NC State.\n\nThe celebrati
 on will include a Sustainability Showcase starting at 8:30 a.m. where you c
 an browse student displays on sustainability-related projects.  Students\, 
  student organizations\, departments and researchers are invited to share t
 heir sustainability-focused research and projects in a science-fair style f
 ormat. Light refreshments will be served during this time. \n\nReserve your
  Sustainability Showcase Spot Here \n\nA recognition program will start by 
 9:30 a.m. and include an announcement of NC State Sustainability Awards win
 ners and NC State Sustainability Fund grant recipients. Following the progr
 am at 10:15 a.m.\, please stay for informal networking. \n\nRSVP to attend 
 the Celebration Here\nThis celebration is one of the hallmark events of NC 
 State's Earth Month and is hosted by the NC State Sustainability Council\, 
 Climate and Sustainability Academy and the University Sustainability Office
 .
DTEND:20260421T143000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025712Z
DTSTART:20260421T123000Z
