 ormation of concept into craftsmanship\, as graduating designers explore fo
 rm\, function and identity through collections developed during their capst
 one course. From refined ready-to-wear to bold avant-garde expressions\, th
 e work reflects both individual vision and technical mastery shaped in the 
 studios and labs of the Wilson College of Textiles.\n\nThe Emerging Designe
 rs Runway Show will be showcased at Talley Student Union.\n\nDoors open at 
 6:30 p.m. Runway show is at 7 p.m.
