BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Retirements\, skills gaps\, and turnover are hitting manufactur
 ing and other industries harder than ever. Join NC State Industry Expansion
  Solutions for a webinar that will outline for employers how to map critica
 l roles\, capture institutional knowledge and build a pipeline of skilled w
 orkers. You'll learn practical tools and strategies to protect your operati
 ons and prepare your company’s next generation of leaders. You should atten
 d the webinar if you are:\n\nA manufacturing or other employer/ownerAn exec
 utiveA plant/training managerAn HR leader who needs to prepare for retireme
 nts\, turnover and talent shortagesParticipants will learn to:\n\nIdentify 
 and develop future leaders within your organizationRetain critical skills a
 nd knowledge before they walk out the doorCreate a succession plan that ali
 gns with their business goals and growthAddress unique workforce challenges
  in manufacturing\, including skills gaps and demographic shifts
DTEND:20260716T150000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025713Z
DTSTART:20260716T140000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Succession Planning Webinar
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51153088928538
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/succession-planning-webinar
END:VEVENT
