BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State University
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Training
DESCRIPTION:Cybersecurity Maturity Model Certification (CMMC) compliance is
  required for all Department of Defense contracts. NC State Industry Expans
 ion Solutions will host a webinar on how to become CMMC compliant\, how lon
 g it takes to become compliant and how much it costs. You should attend the
  webinar if your company is a Department of Defense contractor or plans to 
 become a contractor. Participants will learn:\n\nCMMC is a law\, not an opt
 ional standard.CMMC certification is not an overnight project. CMMC certifi
 cation is not an overnight project. You need to act quickly\, or you will r
 isk losing Department of Defense contracts.
DTEND:20261119T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T025713Z
DTSTART:20261119T150000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Department of Defense Contracting and CMMC Webinar
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51153210168730
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/dod-contracting-cmmc-certification-late
 st-updates-guidance-webinar
END:VEVENT
