DESCRIPTION:The Institutional Biosafety Committee (IBC) invites the NC Stat
 e community to attend our virtual meetings. The IBC provides assurance that
  the potential impacts associated with the intended use of biological organ
 isms at NC State have been appropriately evaluated.\n\nTo receive the meeti
 ng link and additional meeting details\, please contact Brenda L. Mickens a
 t (919) 515-4190.
